      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable ride. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical signs of careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has been kept smoke-free. The leather seats are supple with no rips or stains, showing only light softening on the driver-side bolster. Every electronic component, including the touchscreen navigation, heated seats, and sunroof, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is sound; the engine idles quietly, the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, and the AC blows ice-cold. We have recently performed a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, and the brakes provide confident stopping power. Includes two sets of keys and a folder of recent service receipts.",
